  "remarks": "Army General Oleg Salyukov has been the Commander-in-Chief of the Russian Ground Forces since 2014 and the deputy commander of the Joint Group of Russian Forces since 11 January 2023. As such, he is responsible for Russian ground operations in or to Ukraine. He is also involved in the organisation of patriotic events with the aim of fostering support for the Russian army.",
